Andrew Lawrence (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrew_Lawrence_(actor) 0 Andrew James Lawrence (born January 12, 1988) is an American actor and singer. He is known for his roles as Andy Roman in Brotherly Love and T.J. Detweiler in Recess. Andrew_James_Lawrence ( born January_12_,_1988 ) is an_American_actor_and_singer .
